bassinets.Name: Isla Natural Rattan Bassinet
bassinets.Body:
These vintage inspired baby bassinets are handmade using quality sustainable rattan and create a whimsical place for your little bundle to sleep and a stylish addition to any nursery.

Handmade using natural rattan and as such colour variation can occur.

Mattress included with removable zip cover.

Measures approximately 90cm high x 80cm long x 60cm wide. Bassinet height is approximately 41cm.

We recommend bassinets should not be used once your baby can roll over or pull themselves up (around 4-6 months). Please follow guidelines for SIDS.

Pick up available in Edwardstown South Australia.

bassinets.Name: Tilly Rattan Toddler Bed
bassinets.Body:

Cushion included with cotton cover and zip for removal. 

Measurements approx. 130cm long x 69cm across the base (where the mattress sits). Side height 42cm, end height 70cm high. 

Please note each bed is handmade and may have slight variations.

Available for pick up from Edwardstown Adelaide or please contact us for shipping quote.

bassinets.Name: Hooded Natural Rattan Bassinet
bassinets.Body:

We recommend bassinets should not be used once your baby can roll over or pull themselves up (around 4-6 months). Please follow guidelines for SIDS.

Pick up available from Edwardstown South Australia.

bassinets.Name: Mia Doll Bassinet
bassinets.Body:
